name: Belldandy - Oh My Goddess!
description:
V2.0:

Retrained the LORA. As it was my first LORA, The dataset wasn't as good as I would have liked(I have since gained a lot of experience cleaning datasets). Still some crappy images evaded even this second filter.

Had nice results with: Belldandy, blue_eyes, brown_hair, (facial_mark:1.3), <lora:Belldandy:.45>

Here are some useful tags from the tags summary:

  • long_hair

  • facial_mark

  • forehead_mark

  • blue_eyes

  • jewelry

  • brown_hair

  • smile

  • large_breasts

  • earrings

  • choker

  • bracelet

  • antenna_hair

  • blush

  • ponytail

  • sweat

  • huge_breasts

  • bangle

V1.0:

Her clothes seems to have a strong bias to blue and white.

Got good results with <lora:Bdandy:.4>, (Belldandy), (facial_mark:1.1),
